expression.expression-string: def construct_feature_matrix(wanted_gps, wanted_time, exif_info, wanted_secs, wanted_holiday, wanted_closest_holiday, wanted_city, wanted_city_prop, image_cluster_idx, filter_range=168 * 60 * 60): """construct feature matrix # $\Delta(distance)$, $\Delta(time)$[ from exif "DateTimeDigitized", not from gps], $\Delta(ExposureTime)$, # $\Delta(flash)$, $\Delta(FocalLength)$, $\Delta(ShutterSpeedValue)$, Holiday_idx, nearest_holiday, city freq, # $\Delta(SceneType)$, $\Delta(SensingMethod)$ """ length = int(len(wanted_gps) * (len(wanted_gps) + 1) / 2) features_m = np.empty( shape=(1, 11)) # the first two columns are the idxes of the two images, the last column is label count = 0 for idx_i in range(len(wanted_gps)): for idx_j in range(idx_i, len(wanted_gps)): tmp = np.empty(shape=(1, 15)) if abs((wanted_time[idx_i] - wanted_time[idx_j])[0].total_seconds()) <= filter_range: # feature tmp[0][:2] = [idx_i, idx_j] # index of first event, second event tmp[0][2] = lalong2distance(tuple(wanted_gps[idx_i]), tuple(wanted_gps[idx_j])) # Eclidean distance tmp[0][3] = abs(wanted_secs[idx_i] - wanted_secs[idx_j]) # seconds tmp[0][4] = abs(exif_info[idx_i]["ExposureTime"] - exif_info[idx_j]["ExposureTime"]) # Exposure time tmp[0][5] = abs(exif_info[idx_i]["Flash"] - exif_info[idx_j]["Flash"]) # flash tmp[0][6] = abs(exif_info[idx_i]["FocalLength"] - exif_info[idx_j]["FocalLength"]) # FocalLength tmp[0][7] = abs( exif_info[idx_i]["ShutterSpeedValue"] - exif_info[idx_j]["ShutterSpeedValue"]) # ShutterSpeedValue tmp[0][8] = abs(exif_info[idx_i]["SceneType"] - exif_info[idx_j]["SceneType"]) # SceneType tmp[0][9] = abs( exif_info[idx_i]["SensingMethod"] - exif_info[idx_j]["SensingMethod"]) # SensingMethod # tmp[0][10] = hol_tab[wanted_time[idx_i].strtime("%Y%m%d")][0] # label # holiday?? 0: (0,0), 1: (1,1), 2:(2,2), 3: (1,2) or (2,1), 4:(1,0) or (0,1), 5:(2,0) or (0,2) dict_list = {('0','0') : 0, ('1','1'):1, ('2','2'):2, ('1','2'):3, ('2','1'):3, ('1','0'):4, ('0','1'):4, ('2','0'):5, ('0','2'):5} tmp[0][10] = dict_list[(wanted_holiday[idx_i][0], wanted_holiday[idx_j][0])] # holiday delta time tmp[0][11] = abs(wanted_closest_holiday[idx_i] - wanted_closest_holiday[idx_j]) # holiday average time tmp[0][12] = (wanted_closest_holiday[idx_i] + wanted_closest_holiday[idx_j])/2 # city average proportion tmp[0][13] = (wanted_city_prop[idx_i] + wanted_city_prop[idx_j])/2 if image_cluster_idx[idx_i] == image_cluster_idx[idx_j]: tmp[0][14] = 1 else: tmp[0][14] = 0 features_m = np.append(features_m, tmp, axis=0) count += 1 # print(features_m[-1]) # check label and features # min(features_m[:, 9]) print("Total images: %d, training_samples: %d" % (length, len(features_m))) print("1/0 ratio:", sum(features_m[:, -1] == 1) / len(features_m)) return features_m
